item.title: About Me and The Blog
item.description: Hi There This is my initial post! I am grateful to have a space to share my thoughts and data explorations. In This Blog I’d like to talk about data and analytic and the occasional random rant about things. I will try to express data and my thoughts eleantly (but no promises). Professionally I conisder myself an Experiened Data Professional. I’ve been drawn to data since I started my professional-working career in 2013.
